1
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,680
Matsuda.

2
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,640
I won't let you catch me.

3
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:45,400
Don't panic.

4
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:47,600
Block all exits.

5
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,850
Section Chief Chen.

6
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,800
Protect Captain Matsuda.

7
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,560
Bastard!

8
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,039
What is going on?

9
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:55,560
Go, Captain Matsuda. It's dangerous here.

10
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,000
Boss.

11
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,009
What do we do now?

12
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,600
Back to the Harmonica Club.

13
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:10,800
What about Shen Ling?

14
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,410
Leave her to Chen Yu. Go.

15
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,240
Okay.

16
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,410
Lingzi, Lingzi.

17
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,240
It's me.

18
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,040
Follow me.

19
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,320
Hurry.

20
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:42,880
Here.

21
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,280
Stop right there.

22
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:04,440
Li San.

23
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,610
What do you mean by pointing a gun at me?

24
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:08,840
Chief Chen.

25
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:12,000
Instead of catching Communists in the theater,

26
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,930
where are you going with this girl?

27
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,560
She is my cousin. You don't know her.

28
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:17,720
She is in danger.

29
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,560
I need to protect her.

30
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,890
Stop talking nonsense.

31
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:23,200
The Harmonica Club has been confirmed as a Communist organization.

32
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,329
This cousin of yours

33
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,040
is also a member of the Harmonica Club.

34
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,640
You are involved in this too.

35
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,850
You're biting randomly like a mad dog.

36
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,090
If you have the guts,

37
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:33,120
go confront Captain Matsuda face to face.

38
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,760
Okay.

39
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,920
When Captain Matsuda arrives,

40
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:38,000
you'd better explain to him carefully

41
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,860
what's up with the harmonica in your cousin's hand.

42
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,620
Put your gun on the ground.

43
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,610
Put it on the ground.

44
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:56,960
Don't shoot.

45
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,280
Easy.

46
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,160
Kick it over.

47
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,040
Give me your hand.

48
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,640
Don't move.

49
00:05:06,640 --> 00:05:07,770
Section Chief Chen.

50
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,200
We are all on the same side.

51
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:10,600
There's no need for this.

52
00:05:13,520 --> 00:05:14,280
Is this gun

53
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,530
familiar to you?

54
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,680
You are the one who hit me with that stick.

55
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,810
Now you understand?

56
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,200
It's too late.

57
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,200
Hurry up.

58
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,159
Captain,

59
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,800
the signal is coming from the Harmonica Club.

60
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:45,130
It's very strong and still transmitting.

61
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,240
Stop the car.

62
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,000
In five minutes,

63
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,200
take the Harmonica Club.

64
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,159
I want them alive,

65
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:56,360
and I want that radio.

66
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,280
Yes, sir.

67
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:29,840
Hurry.

68
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,160
Charge in!

69
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:40,080
Charge in, hurry!

70
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,810
How much longer?

71
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,880
Almost done.

72
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,480
Once Lingzi finishes transmitting,

73
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,960
take her and leave through the secret passage immediately.

74
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,840
What about you, Brother?

75
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,040
Don't worry about me.

76
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,160
I'll be right behind you.

77
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:02,600
Brother.

78
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,600
Cut the nonsense.

79
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,340
Keep a close eye on Lingzi.

80
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,480
Go!

81
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,440
I'm done.

82
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,280
Let's go.

83
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,320
Where is Brother?

84
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,520
He told me to take you first. Let's go!

85
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,280
Brother!

86
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,960
- Let's go.
- I'm not leaving.

87
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,159
Listen to Brother!

88
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:54,800
Brother!

89
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,440
Brother!

90
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,920
Lingzi, Lingzi!

91
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:59,400
Brother told me to make sure you stay alive.

92
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,120
Let's go.

93
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,400
Why do so many people

94
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,840
leave their homes

95
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,920
and relentlessly

96
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:05,160
embark on this path?

97
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:11,000
Because we are resisting the invaders.

98
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:13,560
We are protecting our country.

99
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,080
Our music is the bullets.

100
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,560
The broadcasting station is the best chamber.

101
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:25,360
Otherwise,

102
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,520
we can't turn our harmonica club

103
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:28,850
into the second gun against the Japanese.

104
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:41,320
I told my wife.

105
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,520
The radio waves you send out

106
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,240
are the soul of our son

107
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,000
speaking.

108
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,720
You have to be the star

109
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,320
that shines longer.

110
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,080
Sister.

111
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,720
I promise to complete the mission.

112
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,520
Don't worry.

113
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,880
When I get there, I will tell everyone

114
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:05,680
that the harmonica in Harbin is still playing.

115
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,280
In times of national crisis,

116
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,940
we must burn in the dark night.

117
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,420
What we transmit are not radio waves.

118
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,130
What we transmit is the look of spring.

119
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,560
Once spring comes,

120
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:22,840
it won't be so cold anymore.
